  "detailed_description": "You must Bite ALL of the people to make them into Vampires.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCollect ALL Bitecoins.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse Speed Boost to traverse quickly across the Map.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTransform into Goth Vamp.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse a Powerball to stun victims.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDrive a Hearse in a race against time.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFly as a Bat over the City to new heights.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf You are out in the Sunlight too long, You will catch on fire.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBiting People restores some of Your Health.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* This game has Permadeath, so, If You Die or Quit, You have to start over from the beginning. *",
